HDFS Command Cheatsheet

# Starting and Stopping HDFS
start-hdfs.sh
stop-hdfs.sh

# Checking Java Virtual Machine Process Status
jps

# Basic HDFS commands:
hdfs dfs -ls /                      # listing files/directories
hdfs dfs -mkdir /directory          # creating a directory
hdfs dfs -put file /path            # uploading a file to a path
hdfs dfs -cat /path/2/file          # displaying the content of a file

